# See https://help.github.com/articles/ignoring-files/ for more about ignoring files.

# ─── Dependencies ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Matches node_modules in root AND all subdirectories (e.g. agent/node_modules)
**/node_modules
/.pnp
.pnp.*
.yarn/*
!.yarn/patches
!.yarn/plugins
!.yarn/releases
!.yarn/versions

# ─── Next.js ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
/.next/
/out/
/build
next-env.d.ts
*.tsbuildinfo

# ─── Environment & Secrets ───────────────────────────────────────────────────
# NEVER commit secrets. Always use .env.local for local dev.
.env
.env.local
.env.*.local
.env.production
.env.development

# ─── Testing & Coverage ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
/coverage

# ─── Debug & Logs ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
.pnpm-debug.log*
*.log

# ─── OS ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.pem

# ─── Vercel ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.vercel

# ─── Agent system local files ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Skills, mcp.json, AGENTS.md → all tracked (they are documentation, not secrets)
# Ignore only local runtime artifacts if generated:
.codex/logs/
.codex/cache/
